	(11,1,'2013-04-17 01:16:15','2013-04-17 01:16:15','<div class=\"products-container\"><header id=\"page-header\">\r\n<h1>Construction & Agriculture</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"product\">\r\n\r\nConstruction equipment like bulldozers, skid-steers and cranes often work in harsh environments and must meet demanding standards. That’s why durable windshields, laminated glass and door glass are so essential in this segment. Guardian Custom Glass Solutions laminated glass systems play an important role in managing NVH properties and enhancing operator safety and comfort. \r\n\r\nAgricultural equipment is designed to maximize output and field performance while providing comfort during a hard day\'s work. Combine harvesters, row crop tractors, forestry equipment and more are constantly exposed to the elements, spending more days in the field and less time in the barn. Guardian provides infrared reflective glass, solar management glass, heated glass and privacy glass to help combat Mother Nature’s bad side.\r\n\r\n<div style=\"clear:both;width:100%;overflow:auto;padding-top:20px\">\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.customglasssolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/agriculture.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.customglasssolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Forestry_body-copy-Image_344x152.jpg\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>','Construction & Agriculture','','publish','open','open','','construction-and-agriculture','','','2013-04-29 21:22:11','2013-04-29 21:22:11','',0,'http://local.customglass/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),
	(13,1,'2013-04-19 13:45:35','2013-04-19 13:45:35','<div class=\"item-container\"><header id=\"page-header\">\r\n<h1>Solutions For All Your Agriculture Glass Needs</h1>\r\n<p class=\"header-tag\">Thfgfbv fgbvhgn hjguyio mbnjhk sdfertdfg fghrty qwart rty.</p>\r\n\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"featured-container\">\r\n<div class=\"featured-visual\">\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.customglasssolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/video.jpg\" />\r\n\r\nVimi, ni rem il imus excepellabo. Aborcid ta taesid eribus nonsequotem ecereiuunt a.<a title=\"\">Play Video&gt;</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"featured-info\">\r\n<h3>Con/Ag Glass Solutions</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Laminated Glass (bent or flat)\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>- UV Protection Glass</li>\r\n	<li>- Sound Dampening/Acoustic Glass</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Tempered Glass (bent or flat)</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared Reflective Coated Glass</li>\r\n	<li>Heated Glass (wiggle wire or heat grid)</li>\r\n	<li>Insulated Glass</li>\r\n	<li>Branded Glass/Custom Frit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"item\">\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.customglasssolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/tractor.jpg\" />\r\n<h3>Development Capabilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tempered Glass (bent or flat)</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared Reflective Coated Glass</li>\r\n	<li>Heated Glass (wiggle wire or heat grid)</li>\r\n	<li>Insulated Glass</li>\r\n	<li>Branded Glass/Custom Frit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n','Agriculture Glass','','trash','open','open','','agriculture-glass','','','2013-04-29 13:31:34','2013-04-29 13:31:34','',0,'http://local.customglass/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),
