	(405,1,'2013-04-25 05:05:21','2013-04-25 05:05:21','<div class=\"text-container\">\r\n<h1>About</h1>\r\n<p>Guardian’s Custom Glass Solutions group was formed to meet the glass needs of diverse transportation segments such as <a href=\"/commercial-transportation/\" title=\"Commercial Transportation\">commercial</a> & <a href=\"/public-transit/\" title=\"Public Transportation\">public transportation</a>, <a href=\"/construction-and-agriculture/\" title=\"Construction and Agriculture\">construction & agriculture</a>, <a href=\"/safety-and-protection/\" title=\"Safety and Protection\">safety & protection</a>, <a href=\"/lifestyle-vehicles/\" title=\"Lifestyle Vehicles\">lifestyle vehicles</a> and more. Headquartered in Ohio, Custom Glass Solutions manages volumes ranging from 10 parts to 100,000 parts per year, all to serve a diverse set of customers. The group manufactures flat, bent, laminated and tempered glass systems with a dedicated footprint to custom manufacturing. Utilizing the resources of its parent company, <a href=\"http://guardian.com/\" title=\"Guardian Industries\">Guardian Industries</a>, Custom Glass Solutions offers everything from research & development to technical and marketing support required of advanced glass solutions. With full in-house testing capabilities, Custom Glass Solutions ensures all products meet stringent safety and quality regulations as well as specific customer requirements.</p>\r\n<p>Whether it’s small and flat, large and bent or something in between, Guardian has a custom glass solution for you. When you have an idea that involves glass, we have the engineering capabilities to make it a reality. Contact us to learn more.</p>\r\n<p>Learn more about <a href=\"http://guardian.com/\" title=\"Guardian Industries\">Guardian</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2013-04-30 00:47:38','2013-04-30 00:47:38','',0,'http://www.customglasssolutions.com/?page_id=405',0,'page','',0),
